name: Agentic AI Hackathon - Volta (Second Place)
author: Eduard Kakosyan, Huy Huynh, Hao Tang
description: Time Management & Learning assistant with knowledge base for students. Built the main agent responsible for routing and integrating with Google Drive, Calendar, and Email services.

name: SkyPainters - NASA Space Apps Challenge
author: Eduard Kakosyan, Huy Huynh, Hao Tang, Adnan Abdul-Rahim
description: An interactive web application visualizing the night sky from exoplanets using NASA and Gaia DR3 data. Features 3D galaxy model and constellation drawing tools.

name: WebAssembly Particle Simulator
author: Eduard Kakosyan
description: A high-performance particle physics simulator built from scratch in Rust, compiled to WebAssembly for browser execution. Features real-time particle interactions with custom physics engine.
